321
00:12:00,930 --> 00:12:02,432
RIQUINHO DE ESCOLA PARTICULAR
EM NOVA YORK.

322
00:12:02,515 --> 00:12:03,433
RIQUINHO DE SORTE.

323
00:12:03,516 --> 00:12:04,851
