AMÉM.

387
00:14:11,561 --> 00:14:15,523
LUKE:
OK, ENTÃO QUEM QUER
FALAR PRIMEIRO?

388
00:14:15,607 --> 00:14:17,442
(MEMBROS DO GRUPO MURMURAM)

389
00:14:18,568 --> 00:14:19,527
CLARE.

390
00:14:19,611 --> 00:14:21,779
