414
00:15:38,064 --> 00:15:39,440
(CHORA)

415
00:15:39,524 --> 00:15:40,817
CLARE, ESPERE!

416
00:15:40,900 --> 00:15:42,068
(CHORANDO)

417
00:15:43,361 --> 00:15:44,904
