422
00:16:01,171 --> 00:16:03,131
(SUSPIRO TREMULO)

423
00:16:03,214 --> 00:16:04,382
(CHORANDO)

424
00:16:06,926 --> 00:16:08,178
(SUSPIRA PROFUNDAMENTE)

425
